snippet.title: SCP: Nine Tailed Fox Mod - March 2019 Showcase
snippet.description:
This is the March 2019 showcase video of the SCP: Nine Tailed Fox Mod version 0.2.0. This video shows many weapon changes and other improvements.
Isn't that nice?
